  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Suiton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 11 (Spell Level 6)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 10</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 26 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 14 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 28</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> F, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You create a massive wave of water, ready to destroy anything in it's path. The wave travels outward from your location at a speed of 60 ft per round until it reaches its maximum range. The waters in the wave continually rush out in force, causing any Large or smaller sized creature in its area to be pushed back 2d6 x 5 ft and suffer 2d6 water damage. Huge or larger creatures are unaffected. Structures are always affected, and take triple damage, though they are not pushed back.<br><br>If a Raiton technique is used targeting the wave or including the wave inside it's area of effect, the wall is electrified for 1d4+1 rounds, causing it to deal 1d4 electric damage per rank of the Raiton technique used to any creature or structure caught inside the wave.<br><br>If this wave collides with another Suishouha, a Deishouha or a Daibakufu wave, they will cancel each other out.</p>\n\n\n\n",
